backtick 1 1 1 awk '/^MemTotal:/{mt=$2}/^MemFree:/{mf=$2}/SwapTotal:/{st=$2}/^SwapFree:/{sf=$2}END{printf("Mem:%i/%i", (mt-mf)/1024, mt/1024);su=st-sf;if(su)printf("|Swp:%i/%i", su/1024, st/1024)}' /proc/meminfo

backtick 2 1 1 sh -c 'for f in /sys/class/power_supply/BAT*/{charge_{full,now},status}; do echo -e "$(basename $f): $(cat $f)"; done | awk "BEGIN{max=0;now=0;status=\"+\"}/^charge_full:/{max+=\$2}/^charge_now:/{now+=\$2}/^status: Discharging\$/{status=\"-\"}END{result=100.*now/max;if(result>10)printf(\"%s%2.1f%\n\",status,result);else printf(\"%s%i/%i\n\",status,now/1000,max/1000)}"'


shelltitle '$|sh'
shell -$SHELL
vbell off
startup_message off
defscrollback 10000
caption always "%{Gk}%w%=%{Gk}[%{W}%h%{G}]"
hardstatus alwayslastline "%{+b gW}$USER@%H%{dd} %= %{kr}%2`%{g}|%{dd}%l|%1`%{g}|%Y-%m-%d%{c}|%c:%s"
term screen-256color
